Jialong's Blog https://eternityqjl.top/posts/%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0/ -<h2 id="选择排序">选择排序</h2>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="background-color:#fff;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4"><code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"><span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">void</span> <span style="color:#06b;font-weight:bold">selectSort</span>(vector<span style="color:#333">&lt;</span><span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span><span style="color:#333">&gt;&amp;</span> nums) {
	<span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span> n <span style="color:#333">=</span> nums.size();
    <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">for</span> (<span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span> i <span style="color:#333">=</span> <span style="color:#00d;font-weight:bold">0</span>; i <span style="color:#333">&lt;</span> n; i<span style="color:#333">++</span>) {
        <span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span> min <span style="color:#333">=</span> i;
        <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">for</span> (<span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span> j <span style="color:#333">=</span> i<span style="color:#333">+</span><span style="color:#00d;font-weight:bold">1</span>; j <span style="color:#333">&lt;</span> N; j<span style="color:#333">++</span>)
            <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">if</span> (a[j] <span style="color:#333">&lt;</span> a[min]) min <span style="color:#333">=</span> j;
        swap(nums[i], nums[min]);
    }
}
</code></pre></div><h2 id="插入排序">插入排序</h2>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="background-color:#fff;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4"><code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"><span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">void</span> <span style="color:#06b;font-weight:bold">insertSort</span>(vector<span style="color:#333">&lt;</span><span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span><span style="color:#333">&gt;&amp;</span> nums) {
    <span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span> n <span style="color:#333">=</span> nums.size();
    <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">for</span> (<span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span> i <span style="color:#333">=</span> <span style="color:#00d;font-weight:bold">0</span>; i <span style="color:#333">&lt;</span> n; i<span style="color:#333">++</span>) {
        <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">for</span> (<span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span> j <span style="color:#333">=</span> i; j <span style="color:#333">&gt;</span> <span style="color:#00d;font-weight:bold">0</span> <span style="color:#333">&amp;&amp;</span> nums[j] <span style="color:#333">&lt;</span> nums[j<span style="color:#333">-</span><span style="color:#00d;font-weight:bold">1</span>]; j<span style="color:#333">--</span>)
            swap(nums[j], nums[j<span style="color:#333">-</span><span style="color:#00d;font-weight:bold">1</span>]);
    }
}
</code></pre></div><p>时间复杂度为$O(n^2)$，算法稳定。</p>
<h2 id="希尔排序">希尔排序</h2>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="background-color:#fff;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4"><code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"><span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">void</span> <span style="color:#06b;font-weight:bold">shellSort</span>(vector<span style="color:#333">&lt;</span><span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span><span style="color:#333">&gt;&amp;</span> nums) {
    <span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span> n <span style="color:#333">=</span> nums.size();
	<span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span> h <span style="color:#333">=</span> n <span style="color:#333">/</span> <span style="color:#00d;font-weight:bold">2</span>;

    <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">while</span> (h <span style="color:#333">&gt;=</span> <span style="color:#00d;font-weight:bold">1</span>) {
        <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">for</span> (<span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span> i <span style="color:#333">=</span> h; i <span style="color:#333">&lt;</span> n; i<span style="color:#333">++</span>) {
            <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">for</span> (<span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span> j <span style="color:#333">=</span> i; j <span style="color:#333">&gt;=</span> h <span style="color:#333">&amp;&amp;</span> num[j] <span style="color:#333">&lt;</span> nums[j<span style="color:#333">-</span>h]; j <span style="color:#333">-=</span> h)
                swap(nums[j], nums[j<span style="color:#333">-</span>h]);
        }
        h <span style="color:#333">=</span> h<span style="color:#333">/</span><span style="color:#00d;font-weight:bold">2</span>;
    }
}
</code></pre></div><p>n在某个特定范围内时，希尔排序的时间复杂度约为$O(n^{1.3})$，最坏时间复杂度为$O(n^2)$。算法不稳定。</p>
<h2 id="冒泡排序">冒泡排序</h2>
<p>从后向前两两比较相邻元素的值。</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="background-color:#fff;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4"><code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"><span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">void</span> <span style="color:#06b;font-weight:bold">BubbleSort</span>(vector<span style="color:#333">&lt;</span><span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span><span style="color:#333">&gt;&amp;</span> nums) {
    <span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span> n <span style="color:#333">=</span> nums.size();
    <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">for</span> (<span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span> i <span style="color:#333">=</span> <span style="color:#00d;font-weight:bold">0</span>; i <span style="color:#333">&lt;</span> n; i<span style="color:#333">++</span>) {
        <span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span> flag <span style="color:#333">=</span> <span style="color:#007020">false</span>;	<span style="color:#888">//flag用来判断一趟遍历是否发生交换，如果没有发生交换则说明已经有序
</span><span style="color:#888"></span>        <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">for</span> (<span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span> j <span style="color:#333">=</span> i; j <span style="color:#333">&lt;</span> n <span style="color:#333">-</span> <span style="color:#00d;font-weight:bold">1</span>; j<span style="color:#333">++</span>) {
            <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">if</span> (nums[j] <span style="color:#333">&lt;</span> nums[j<span style="color:#333">+</span><span style="color:#00d;font-weight:bold">1</span>]) {
                swap(nums[j], nums[j<span style="color:#333">+</span><span style="color:#00d;font-weight:bold">1</span>]);
                flag <span style="color:#333">=</span> <span style="color:#007020">true</span>;
            }
            <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">if</span> (flag <span style="color:#333">==</span> <span style="color:#007020">false</span>)
                <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">return</span>;
        }
    }
}
</code></pre></div><p>时间复杂度：$O(n^2)$，算法稳定。</p>
<h2 id="快速排序">快速排序</h2>
<p>递归调用。</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="background-color:#fff;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4"><code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"><span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">void</span> <span style="color:#06b;font-weight:bold">quickSort</span>(vector<span style="color:#333">&lt;</span><span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span><span style="color:#333">&gt;&amp;</span> nums, <span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span> low, <span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span> high) {
	<span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">if</span> (low <span style="color:#333">&lt;</span> high) {
        <span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span> pivot <span style="color:#333">=</span> partition(nums, low, high);
        quickSort(nums, low, pivot <span style="color:#333">-</span> <span style="color:#00d;font-weight:bold">1</span>);
        quickSort(nums, pivot <span style="color:#333">+</span> <span style="color:#00d;font-weight:bold">1</span>, high);
    }
}
<span style="color:#888">//每趟划分都把当前数组第一个元素作为轴枢，把所有小于轴枢的元素移动到左侧，大于轴枢的元素移动到右侧
</span><span style="color:#888"></span><span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span> <span style="color:#06b;font-weight:bold">partition</span>(vector<span style="color:#333">&lt;</span><span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span><span style="color:#333">&gt;&amp;</span> nums, <span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span> low, <span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span> high) {
    <span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span> pivot <span style="color:#333">=</span> nums[low];	<span style="color:#888">//将第一个元素当作轴枢，low和high作为两个指针
</span><span style="color:#888"></span>    <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">while</span> (low <span style="color:#333">&lt;</span> high) {
        <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">while</span> (low <span style="color:#333">&lt;</span> high <span style="color:#333">&amp;&amp;</span> nums[high] <span style="color:#333">&gt;=</span> pivot)	<span style="color:#333">--</span>high;
        nums[low] <span style="color:#333">=</span> nums[high];	<span style="color:#888">//将比轴枢小的元素移动到左端
</span><span style="color:#888"></span>        <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">while</span> (low <span style="color:#333">&lt;</span> high <span style="color:#333">&amp;&amp;</span> nums[low] <span style="color:#333">&lt;=</span> pivot)	<span style="color:#333">++</span>low;
        nums[high] <span style="color:#333">=</span> nums[low];	<span style="color:#888">//将比轴枢大的元素移动到右侧
</span><span style="color:#888"></span>    }
    <span style="color:#888">//结束时low==high
</span><span style="color:#888"></span>    nums[low] <span style="color:#333">=</span> pivot;
    <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">return</span> low;
}
</code></pre></div><p>时间复杂度为$O(n\log_2 n)$。算法不稳定。</p>
<h2 id="归并排序">归并排序</h2>
<p>2路归并排序。分治的思想。</p>
<p>归并排序必须要占用额外的存储空间，空间复杂度为O(N)</p>
<h3 id="自顶向下归并">自顶向下归并</h3>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="background-color:#fff;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4"><code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp">vector<span style="color:#333">&lt;</span><span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span><span style="color:#333">&gt;</span> aux;
<span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">void</span> <span style="color:#06b;font-weight:bold">mergeSort</span>(vector<span style="color:#333">&lt;</span><span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span><span style="color:#333">&gt;&amp;</span> nums, <span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span> low, <span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span> high) {
    <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">if</span>(low <span style="color:#333">&lt;</span> high) {
        <span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span> mid <span style="color:#333">=</span> (low <span style="color:#333">+</span> high) <span style="color:#333">/</span> <span style="color:#00d;font-weight:bold">2</span>;
        MergeSort(nums, low, mid);
        MergeSort(nums, mid<span style="color:#333">+</span><span style="color:#00d;font-weight:bold">1</span>, high);
        Merge(A, low, mid, high);
    }
}
<span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">void</span> <span style="color:#06b;font-weight:bold">Merge</span>(vector<span style="color:#333">&lt;</span><span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span><span style="color:#333">&gt;&amp;</span> nums, <span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span> low, <span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span> mid, <span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span> high) {
    <span style="color:#888">//nums中的两段nums[low, mid]和nums[mid + 1, high]各自有序，将这两个数组合并
</span><span style="color:#888"></span>    <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">for</span> (<span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span> m <span style="color:#333">=</span> low; m <span style="color:#333">&lt;=</span> high; m<span style="color:#333">++</span>) {
        aux.push_back(nums[m]);
    }
    <span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span> i <span style="color:#333">=</span> <span style="color:#00d;font-weight:bold">0</span>, j <span style="color:#333">=</span> mid <span style="color:#333">-</span> low <span style="color:#333">+</span> <span style="color:#00d;font-weight:bold">1</span>;
    <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">for</span> (<span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span> k <span style="color:#333">=</span> low; k <span style="color:#333">&lt;=</span> high; k<span style="color:#333">++</span>) {
        <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">if</span> (i <span style="color:#333">&gt;</span> mid <span style="color:#333">-</span> low)					nums[k] <span style="color:#333">=</span> aux[j<span style="color:#333">++</span>];
        <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">else</span> <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">if</span> (j <span style="color:#333">&gt;</span> high <span style="color:#333">-</span> low)			nums[k] <span style="color:#333">=</span> aux[i<span style="color:#333">++</span>];
        <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">else</span> <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">if</span> (aux[j] <span style="color:#333">&lt;=</span> aux[i])			nums[k] <span style="color:#333">=</span> aux[j<span style="color:#333">++</span>];
        <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">else</span>								nums[k] <span style="color:#333">=</span> aux[i<span style="color:#333">++</span>];
    }
}
</code></pre></div><h3 id="自底向上归并">自底向上归并</h3>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="background-color:#fff;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4"><code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp">vector<span style="color:#333">&lt;</span><span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span><span style="color:#333">&gt;</span> aux;
<span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">void</span> <span style="color:#06b;font-weight:bold">mergeSort</span>(vector<span style="color:#333">&lt;</span><span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span><span style="color:#333">&gt;&amp;</span> nums, <span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span> low, <span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span> high) {
    <span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span> N <span style="color:#333">=</span> nums.size();
    <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">for</span> (<span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span> sz <span style="color:#333">=</span> <span style="color:#00d;font-weight:bold">1</span>; sz <span style="color:#333">&lt;</span> N; sz <span style="color:#333">=</span> sz <span style="color:#333">+</span> sz) {	<span style="color:#888">//sz为子数组的大小
</span><span style="color:#888"></span>        <span style="color:#080;font-weight:bold">for</span> (<span style="color:#339;font-weight:bold">int</span> lo <span style="color:#333">=</span> <span style="color:#00d;font-weight:bold">0</span>; lo <span style="color:#333">&lt;</span> N <span style="color:#333">-</span> sz; lo <span style="color:#333">+=</span> sz <span style="color:#333">+</span> sz) {	<span style="color:#888">//lo为子数组的索引
</span><span style="color:#888"></span>            Merge(nums, lo, lo<span style="color:#333">+</span>sz<span style="color:#333">-</span><span style="color:#00d;font-weight:bold">1</span>, MIN(lo<span style="color:#333">+</span>sz<span style="color:#333">+</span>sz<span style="color:#333">-</span><span style="color:#00d;font-weight:bold">1</span>, N<span style="color:#333">-</span><span style="color:#00d;font-weight:bold">1</span>));
        }
    }
}
</code></pre></div><p>自底向上归并会多次遍历整个数组，根据子数组的大小进行两两归并。子数组的大小sz的初始值为1，每次加倍。最后一个子数组的大小只有在数组大小是sz的偶数倍时才会等于sz（否则其会比sz小）。</p>
<p>归并排序是一种渐进最优的基于比较的排序算法。在最坏的情况下的比较次数为$n\log n$.</p>
